law.history: Repealed 2002 Ky. Acts ch. 283, sec. 20, effective July 15, 2002. -- Amended 1982 Ky. Acts ch. 377. sec. 4, effective July 15, 1982. -- Amended 1978 Ky. Acts ch. 155, sec. 32, effective June 17, 1978. -- Created 1972 Ky. Acts ch. 353, sec. 16.
